title: Week 3 preview & Redskins vs. Giants recap
itunes:title: Week 3 preview & Redskins vs. Giants recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – recap the Thursday Night Football matchup between the Washington Redskins and the New York Giants. Then, the heroes welcome in Andrew Siciliano to breakdown each week 3 matchup.
